                    <p
                      style="margin: 10px 0;padding: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #202020;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;">A new year is upon us, and we are hopeful for a safe and productive season with a full calendar of racing!</p>

                    <h2 class="null"
                      style="display: block;margin: 0;padding: 0;color: #202020;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 22px;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;line-height: 125%;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;">2022 Season</h2>

                    <p
                      style="margin: 10px 0;padding: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #202020;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;">Live, in person racing is back! Our tireless race directors are hard at work getting a full calendar of races permitted and ready to go. The first race of the season is the Makaha Time Trial on February 19th run by
                      <a href="https://www.hitricenter.com/makaha-time-trial" target="_blank"
                        style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #007C89;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;">Hawaii Triathlon Center</a> and
                      <a href="https://flpregister.com/568" target="_blank"
                        style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #007C89;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;">registration is now open</a>. We would like to issue a special thank you to Ben Williams of Hawaii Triathlon Center for his persistent&nbsp;advocacy over the last two years to bring bicycle racing and triathlons back to Oahu! The full calendar is available
                      <a href="https://asbra.org/calendar/" target="_blank"
                        style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #007C89;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;">on our website</a>, but here are the details for the first few:
                    </p>

                    <ul>
                      <li
                        style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;">Makaha Time Trial - Saturday February 19th -
                        <a href="https://flpregister.com/568" target="_blank"
                          style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #007C89;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;">Register Now</a>
                      </li>
                      <li
                        style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;">Pineapple Sprint - Sunday March 6th
                      </li>
                      <li
                        style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;">Castle to Hanauma Bay Time Trial - Sunday March 20th
                      </li>
                      <li
