                    <p
                      style="margin: 10px 0;padding: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #202020;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;">The annual Oahu Hill Climb Challenge, organized by
                      <a href="https://tradewindcyclingteam.com/" target="_blank"
                        style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #007C89;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;">Tradewind Cycling Team</a>, is going on
                      <strong>right now</strong>&nbsp;through the end of February. <a href="https://www.ohcc.xyz/"
                        target="_blank"
                        style="mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #007C89;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;">Register now</a> using your Strava account and start the season strong&nbsp;tackling 8 epic climbs.
                    </p>

